
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 07 of Thoracic MRT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Clavicle fracture' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled
And 'AO Classification' checkbox is enabled
And 'Rockwood' checkbox is enabled
And 'Tossy' checkbox is enabled

//AO Classification
When I select 'AO Classification' checkbox
Then '15.1: Medial end segment' radio button is enabled
And '15.2 Diaphyseal segment' radio button is enabled
And '15.3: Lateral end segment' radio button is enabled
And '15: Not further specified' radio button is enabled

When I select '15.1: Medial end segment' radio button
Then '15.1A' radio button is enabled
And '15.1B' radio button is enabled
And '15.1C' radio button is enabled

When I select '15.2 Diaphyseal segment' radio button
Then '15.2A' radio button is enabled
And '15.2B' radio button is enabled
And '15.2C' radio button is enabled

When I select '15.3: Lateral end segment' radio button
Then '15.3A' radio button is enabled
And '15.3B' radio button is enabled
And '15.3C' radio button is enabled

When I select '15: Not further specified' radio button
Then 'Fracture older, consolidated' radio button is enabled
And 'Suspected' radio button is enabled

//Rockwood
When I select 'Rockwood' checkbox
Then 'Grade 1' radio button is enabled
And 'Grade 2' radio button is enabled
And 'Grade 3' radio button is enabled
And 'Grade 4' radio button is enabled
And 'Grade 5' radio button is enabled
And 'Grade 6' radio button is enabled

//Tossy
When I select 'Tossy' checkbox
Then 'Tossy 1' radio button is enabled
And 'Tossy 2' radio button is enabled
And 'Tossy 3' radio button is enabled
